
       ----------------


       Challenge Description:

       [IMAGE]

       Write a program which capitalizes the first letter of each word in
       a sentence.


       Input sample:

       Your program should accept as its first argument a path to a
       filename. Input example is the following

       Hello world javaScript language a letter 1st thing


       Output sample:

       Print capitalized words in the following way.

       Hello World JavaScript Language A Letter 1st Thing

   